private approach conducted by PROGIS, Adcon, forCert
*16 -- 17 November - ENTEBBE, Uganda
To realize a green revolution for Africa, experts mentioned the 
importance of TECHNOLOGY; further the must of more INTEGRATION and 
COOPERATION and better PLANNING together with increased ADVISORY 
SERVICES for a successful uptake. A group of European companies, highly 
dedicated to boost agricultural development, brought all these elements 
together and will introduce an integrated model for land-, farm- and 
forest management mid of November in Entebbe/Uganda. Integrated stands 
for technology cooperation, for farmers integration into cooperative 
tasks, for horizontal and vertical sector integration, the integration 
of advisory support and for the integration of financing institutes and 
insurance companies, which became possible with the help of 
sophisticated technology.

If you are farmer, belonging to a farm advisory group, or buyer of farm 
products , seller of machines, crops or chemicals to farmers, or if you 
are consultant, or forester, or working in the agro-finance sector (e.g. 
