                      <b>Manic depression?<br>
                      </b>The psychology instructor had just finished a
                      lecture on mental health and was giving an oral
                      test.<br>
                      <br>
                      Speaking specifically about manic depression, she
                      asked, "How would you diagnose a patient who walks
                      back and forth screaming at the top of his lungs
                      one minute, then sits in a chair weeping
                      uncontrollably the next?"<br>
                      <br>
                      A young man in the rear raised his hand and
                      answered, "A basketball coach?"<br>
